EDq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GTEEDq.png&h=a1107013&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65eaa66b71b25d0ddac5402d1096020ac8b56080","tid":2438194,"uid":66557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:46:50.000Z","msg":"佢唔似噤短命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁借問聲我有幾長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個仔係打科興打死嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e599395236e4846c949db4bf9dd046de6ab2217f","tid":2438194,"uid":47775,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b63b7b2ef47ec0621c341c3eee6c01bd010a1e51","tid":2438194,"uid":2054,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"96cdb12ed3b75cc98051548c87cd89f61e2caf90","tid":2438194,"uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:43:58.000Z","msg":"點先算有直接關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:44:42.000Z","msg":"怎樣才算打科興而死<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:47:12.000Z","msg":"同點樣先算正式贏到巴塞一樣"},{"pid":"d4cd14687a1c746cd04e441e0ae184197bb6a9d5","tid":2438194,"uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://therepublikofmancunia.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/RvP-Reading-GIF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftherepublikofmancunia.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F12%2FRvP-Reading-GIF.gif&h=e3cd80c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96d1edd476b9450562ebabd61cb753f32f236478","tid":2438194,"uid":102356,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:48:14.000Z","msg":"怎樣才算與接種疫苗有關係?<br />\n<br />\n1.要在身體顛峰期接種<br />\n2.要在身體內部沒有毛病的時候接種<br />\n3.要在身體狀態最好的時候接種<br />\n4.你不能有糖尿病<br />\n5.你不能有高血壓、高血脂、中央肥胖<br />\n6.你不能患有嚴重神經系統疾病<br />\n7.你不能是處於懷孕期或哺乳期的女性<br />\n8.你不能是未能控制病情的嚴重慢性病患者<br />\n9.你不能有嚴重過敏病史，包括對疫苗內活性成分過敏；以及曾對其他疫苗有急性過敏反應、呼吸困難等<br />\n10.醫護打疫苗，你不能幾個親友去攔截，要讓護士順利接種<br />\n11.你不能是16歲以下嬰幼兒、兒童及青少年<br />\n12.你完整的病歷紀錄要被在場每個醫護都看過一遍，最好被門外兩個保安都過看一遍，然後再將報告送到衞生防護中心，這樣才是真穩妥，否則會被視為是個別事件<br />\n13.你的照顧者/陪同人士在接種中心不能大聲喧譁<br />\n14.你要允許醫護人員於你在中心休息的30分鐘內進醫療室交流<br />\n15.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你死了，個別單位也會說你是特殊案例，說你是不幸，說無可疑。XXX總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該死亡。"},{"pid":"e0244f8bdfef0b246d50c3a504e30acd19ba3782","tid":2438194,"uid":383204,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bG5GSY5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbG5GSY5.jpg&h=caf5b2a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9a0b1feb1d4771b8bc9578fd833a84c1f05ef62","tid":2438194,"uid":213142,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11d899e1ee9b4144c80ef6c5fd236961204b6d9","tid":2438194,"uid":80902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a20b0b40b3b43b430c014a2077aaed3201b2f6d2","tid":2438194,"uid":8821,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:43:57.000Z","msg":"除非直接打支毒劑比你，否則都好難有所以直接關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打完之後即死都係唔關事"},{"pid":"911df5a6c8e1515bb39d1ee0054a7725d4c6fa9b","tid":2438194,"uid":20805,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"6f165decc560413271f33f384699e018e8d64e29","tid":2438194,"uid":380132,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:45:41.000Z","msg":"班香港專家都幾癲，係咪望幾下數據就話唔關事<br />\n連解剖都冇咁嘅需要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9B036jy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9B036jy.jp