當時所有人都懷疑係同啲電線裏面嘅鉛有關。但電線廠拎出化驗報告證明電線內銅線嘅含鉛量超低，不足以構成該病人體內極高嘅鉛含量。<br />\n4. 但醫生相信病人體內嘅嘅鉛含量過高，係同該工人習慣用口咬電線有關。但電線嚟嘅金屬銅又真係冇乜鉛喎。當時電線廠話「冇證據顯示病人體內嘅高含鉛量係同接觸電線有關」。咁當然唔使賠償啦！<br />\n5. 最後發現原來啲鉛唔係金屬銅裏面，而係喺包住電線嘅絕緣體pvc膠皮裏面。當時一般 PVC 膠含 2%-5% 鉛嘅鹽作為穩定劑同色母，而工人習慣用口咬走咗包住電線嘅PVC膠皮去駁電線同電器，咁體內就多咗好多鉛！<br />\n科學家唔應該咁武斷呢！"},{"pid":"4d6b01a0dc42996505938474f91acf8a04aaba44","tid":2438194,"uid":132625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:11:25.000Z","msg":"真係得弱智仔先打支那疫苗<br />\n諗落算係另類 natural selection <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744158cd1264108465abdb4ff6d701bf1e403e38","tid":2438194,"uid":152180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6107a01b9f71280b731eb2e1d2977e1821c42b07","tid":2438194,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:03:42.000Z","msg":"而家死左幾多個?4個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:11:36.000Z","msg":"呢個好似係第二個"},{"pid":"59c2354788ea9ed321378ebf5bd57e562c56ad79","tid":2438194,"uid":115096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96cdb12ed3b75cc98051548c87cd89f61e2caf90","tid":2438194,"uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:43:58.000Z","msg":"點先算有直接關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:11:50.000Z","msg":"一拮入去即時慘叫一聲 &ldquo;哎吔！&rdquo; <br />\n插住支針即場斷氣<br />\n如果抆咗支針出嚟先慘叫斷氣都唔算"},{"pid":"f846c96a059297e1bee17a5a864ee12f1b517313","tid":2438194,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eo0cfjJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feo0cfjJ.gif&h=6d67bcaa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4c587e69da56497555031bb01fb789677dc8689","tid":2438194,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep